text:
Volleyball sub-state schedule for area schools By ADAM GARDNER Atchison Globe   
Sub-state action will take place Saturday, Oct. 24 for area high school volleyball teams. 
In the Class 3A sub-state held at Marysville, Maur Hill-Mount Academy's 26-10 record earned the Ravens the No. 1 seed.
